        Parameters:

      • clickInHand

        public void clickInHand(LogicHandler handler,
                        int slot)
        Description copied from class: Card
        What happens when a card is clicked in hand. Minions go to their own chosen-variable, others will have their own when implemented.
        Specified by:
        clickInHand in class Card
        Parameters:
        handler - LogicHandler.
        slot - Slot in hand.

      • clickInTable

        public void clickInTable(LogicHandler handler,
                         int slot)
        What happens when a minion is clicked in a table. Changes the location of the minion and sets it chosen in the handler. This could be moved over to LogicHandler too.
        Parameters:
        handler - LogicHandler.
        slot - The minion's slot in table.

      • enterTable

        public void enterTable(Player ownPlayer,
                       Player enemyPlayer,
                       int slot)
        What happens when a minion enters the table. This method can be Overrided to add special table entering effects to minion.
        Parameters:
        ownPlayer - Player whose turn it is.
        enemyPlayer - The other player.
        slot - Slot where the minion is put in table.

      • die

        public void die()
        What happens when a minion dies. This method can be Overrided to add special dying effects to minion.
